## Reflection

### The Responsibility Pledge

Take a few minutes to translate today's leadership concepts into actionable commitments.

1. **Identify Your Network:** Write down the names of three people in your immediate "Network" (at the hub, in your studies, or in your community) who you collaborate with frequently.
2. **Take Responsibility:** Write a short pledge outlining one specific action you will take this week to practice "idealized influence" or support their professional development.
3. **Audit Your Style:** Discuss your pledge with your Habit Buddy. Ask them to give you honest feedback on whether your daily communication style tends to lean more toward High Power Distance (telling people what to do) or Low Power Distance (encouraging their initiative and psychological safety).

